## Rules
- Keep flat structure (no nesting)
- No descriptions/comments per entry
- Use exact function names
- Update only on function/file change
- Prefer less data, avoid noise

---

## Agent Usage
1. Find function in [FUNCTIONS]
2. Jump to file
3. Check [USAGE] for impact
4. Follow [GRAPH] for call chain

---

## Goal
Fast navigation + minimal tokens